PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776258665
OL,3,CRobert Burns' family flute played in
OL,4,CNew York to help save poet's home
OL,6,FJoan McAlpine, Project Director of the
OL,7,Ftrust said: "Americans have made Auld
OL,8,FLang Syne into one of the most famous
OL,9,Fsongs in the world - an international
OL,10,Fanthem to friendship.
OL,12,F"Now we are asking them to join hands
OL,13,Fwith us, in the spirit of the song, to
OL,14,Fsave the very special place where it
OL,15,Fwas created."
OL,17,FBurns penned around a third of his
OL,18,Flife's work at Ellisland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
