PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776258665
OL,3,CRobert Burns' family flute played in
OL,4,CNew York to help save poet's home
OL,6,FTraditional flautist Claire Mann has
OL,7,Fthe honour of playing the flute, being
OL,8,Fthe only musician the charity has
OL,9,Fentrusted with handling the historic
OL,10,Finstrument.
OL,12,FAlongside Ms Mann, award-winning
OL,13,FScottish singer Robyn Stapleton and
OL,14,Fharpist Rebecca Hill will perform
OL,15,Fsongs composed at Ellisland.
OL,17,FClaire Mann said: "Every time I play
OL,18,Fthis flute, I'm aware of how much
OL,19,Fhistory it holds.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
