FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776258665
OL,3,CRobert Burns' family flute played in
OL,4,CNew York to help save poet's home
OL,6,F"To play this instrument in front of
OL,7,FRobert Burns's statue in Central Park
OL,8,Fwill be a moment I'll never forget."
OL,10,FThe team behind Ellisland Farm will
OL,11,Falso join the NYC Tartan Day Parade on
OL,12,FSaturday April 11, which will make its
OL,13,Fway from West 44th to 55th Street.
OL,15,FThe visit to New York has been
OL,16,Fsupported by the National Lottery
OL,17,FHeritage Fund, which has awarded the
OL,18,Fcharity a grant to help kick-start an
OL,19,Finternational fundraising campaign.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
